y, such many-body\neffects can also be employed in work extraction and refrigeration protocols at\nquantum scale.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 18 Aug 2019 17:38:54 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 28 Aug 2019 22:44:26 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-08-05"}
