t of superradiance, a mechanism\nthat extracts rotational energy from the black hole. Orbital signatures for the\nS2 star are computed and shown to be detectable by GRAVITY. The scalar field\ncan be constrained because the variation of orbital elements depends both on\nthe relative mass of the scalar field to the black hole and on the field mass\ncoupling parameter.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 19 Aug 2019 10:13:42 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 9 Sep 2019 16:47:28 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-09-10"}
