T \\approx 10^5$ K, with size comparable to\nthat of the hot slab, above the post-shock region. At larger distances the\ntemperature gradually decreases to $T \\approx 10^4$ K.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 19 Aug 2019 13:48:08 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 20 Aug 2019 07:52:39 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-09-18"}
